### -----------------------------------------------
### ALLOTMENTS (Room Blocks for Groups/Events)
### -----------------------------------------------

### List All Allotments
# @name listAllotments
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/allotments?tenant_id={{tenantId}}&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### List Allotments by Status
# @name listAllotmentsByStatus
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/allotments?tenant_id={{tenantId}}&status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

